    "This manual, frequency-based selection may also capture media salience rather than genuine economic or financial linkages, potentially impacting the accuracy of modeling inter-company sentiment spillovers.",
    "More robust, data-driven approaches such as graph community detection, price correlation networks, or industry classification proximity offer promising alternatives and will be investigated in future studies to improve model robustness and generalizability.",
